CIRCULAR
• Highest dynamic performance.
• Best force symmetry.
• Best for premium high-performance applications.

RECTANGULAR 2×3
• Simplest to manufacture.
• Lowest production cost.
• Excellent for scalable industrial production.

FRONTAL OPPOSED
• Best compromise between compactness, cooling, maintenance and performance.
• Particularly well suited to compact electro-hydraulic propulsion systems where
  packaging volume is critical.

For the current VHX-220 concept, the Frontal Opposed 3VS3 architecture is the
strongest baseline because it balances manufacturability, serviceability,
thermal management and structural performance while remaining compatible with
future upgrades.

